---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Smart Poultry - Real-time poultry health monitoring to reduce mortality, improve production, and empower farmers."
  title="Smart Poultry | SmartIView"
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-[120px] bg-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto">

      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12 bg-gray-200">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black-800 mb-4">Smart Poultry</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
         Transforming poultry farming through smart technology.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Overview (with photo) -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <img src="/assets/solutions/smartpoultry.jpg" alt="Smart Poultry Overview" class="mb-4 md:mb-0 md:mr-8 w-full md:w-1/2 rounded-lg shadow-md" />
          <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Overview</h2>
            <p class="text-base text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Smart Poultry is an intelligent poultry farm monitoring system developed by SmartIView to tackle one of Nigeria's pressing agricultural challenges - high bird mortality, disease spread, and poor productivity due to lack of real-time insights.
              <br>
              Our solution combines IoT sensors, cloud-based analytics, and mobile/web dashboards to empower farmers with data-driven decisions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Benefits -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Key Benefits</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-black-800">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">1. Real-time Monitoring</h3>
              <p>
                Track temperature, humidity, ammonia levels, and general environmetal conditions to ensure optimal bird health.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">2. Early Warning Alerts</h3>
              <p>
                Get notified instantly of abnormal conditions to prevent losses and respond quickly.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">3. Health insights</h3>
              <p>
                Visual reports on bird behaviour, feeding patterns, and environmental trends to identify potential issues early.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1">4. Data-Driven Decisions</h3>
              <p>
                Access daily/weekly performance analytics, anytime - via your smartphone or web dashboard.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- How It Works -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
          <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-black-600 mb-4">
            <li>Sensors Installed in poultry houses to monitor key health parameters.</li>
            <br>
            <li>Data Transmitted securely to the cloud in real-time.</li>
            <br>
            <li>Analytical Engine interprets trends and raises alerts when needed.</li>
            <br>
            <li>User Dashboard (web/mobile) allows farmers and stakeholders to track health, productivity, and take action.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Designed For & Impact Focus (merged) -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4">Designed For:</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-black-800 mb-4">
            <li>Poultry Farm Owners</li>
            <br>
            <li>Cooperatives</li>
            <br>
            <li>Agricultural Extension Officers</li>
            <br>
            <li>NGOs & Government Agencies</li>
            <br>
            <li>Agritech Investors</li>
           </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

          <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Impact Focus</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-black-800">
            <li>Reduce bird mortality</li>
            <br>
            <li>Increase farm productivity</li>
            <br>
            <li>Empower rural farmers with smart tools</li>
            <br>
            <li>Promote food security across Nigeria and beyond</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Want to Partner? -->
      <div class="w-full mb-12">
        <div class="bg-blue-100 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">Want to Partner?</h2>
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block py-3 px-6 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition duration-300 mt-2">Become a Partner</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>